title: We Are Still Open Through Road Construction. Get Up to $500 OFF!*
posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', "ROAD CONTRUCTION SPECIAL: Don't let the road construction detour you, we are open!", 'Apply for your new home the same day you tour & receive $300 OFF a 2 BR or $500 OFF a 3 BR!*', '*Some income and other restrictions may apply.', 'Please call for more details.', 'Offer valid when you apply by 8/5/2022 and move-in by 8/15/2022.', 'We have everything you want at a fantastic price with our 1, 2, or 3 bedroom apartments.', 'With gallery-style kitchens, huge closets, and spacious floorplans, we have everything you need.', 'Located just a short-drive from the Minneapolis metro area, the opportunities are endless at Albertville Meadows!', 'We have the keys to your new beginning!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Handicapped Accessible (Select Homes)', '- Galley Style Kitchens With Plenty Of Space', '- Master Suite Walk-In Closet (Select Homes)', '- Ample Off-Street Open Parking', '- New Biking Trail', '- Utilities Included: Heat, Water, Sewer, Trash', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Albertville Meadows Apartments participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:10:30AM-5:00PM', 'Make the move today by giving our professional staff a call:', 'show contact info', 'Albertville Meadows', '10732 County Road 37 NE', 'Albertville, MN, 55301', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'VtWqq1h1']
